      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This worked for me: in Eclipse go to Preferences -&gt; Maven (No subcategory). Check   - &quot;Download artifact Source&quot;  - &quot;Download artifact JavaDocs&quot;  - &quot;Update Maven projects on startup&quot; (just because I can&#39;t find the manual way) Then restart Eclipse. Done"
