    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case the \"settings.xml\" solution didn't work so I use this command in order to download all the sources:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn dependency:sources\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You also can use it with other maven commands, for example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn clean install dependency:sources -Dmaven.test.skip=true\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>To download all documentation, use the following command:</p>\n\n<pre><code>mvn dependency:resolve -Dclassifier=javadoc\n</code></pre>\n"
