  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/5780758/maven-always-download-sources-and-javadocs",
  "title" : "Maven – Always download sources and javadocs",
  "body" : "<p>Is there a way I can configure maven to <em>always</em> download sources and javadocs? Specifying <code>-DdownloadSources=true -DdownloadJavadocs=true</code> everytime (which usually goes along with running <code>mvn compile</code> twice because I forgot the first time) becomes rather tedious.</p>\n"
